      <p>US1 Travel can be designated as a “Travel Management Company” licensed by ARC & IATA for more than 25 years. The Company was founded in December of 1987. Once a small Retail Agency serving the local Community, we were known as “The L.A. Connection Travel”. We primarily served small corporate accounts and leisure travelers peaking in 1997 with 2million dollars in Gross sales. In 1989 We launched “Travel Net” a bulletin board online information and media tool running on an AST 386 computer and two Hayes 9600Baud modems. This was several years prior to the internet and offered Tech Savvy consumers a medium to search flight schedules, see fares and search out package vacations. Travel net operated uninterrupted for nearly 4 years with more than 200 users in the Los Angeles area. In 1994 The Company changed direction in soliciting independent contractors to work from Home using dial up modems as a means of connectivity. This represented the first such time an Agent could use the professional reservation system and make bookings directly with a Host Location. For the following three years between 1994 and 1997 more than 30 independent Agents signed agreements to work exclusively with The L.A. Connection. We provided training onsite and through manuals written exclusively for this Affiliate program.</p>

